Hi. I had the same problem. In my project I make simple workaround, like this.
`
class FixedPolymorphicQuerySet(PolymorphicQuerySet):

    def order_by(self, *args, **kwargs):
        new_args = [
            translate_polymorphic_field_path(self.model, a)
            if hasattr(a, 'partition') else a
            for a in args
        ]
        return super(PolymorphicQuerySet, self).order_by(*new_args, **kwargs)


class FixedPolymorphicManager(PolymorphicManager):
    queryset_class = FixedPolymorphicQuerySet
`
